{"tid":1624654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日究竟有冇人搞議員辦事處同政府合署","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:06:13.000Z","uid":60423,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4f41882c3b14716380474ba988c593db320a8cc1","tid":1624654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"我知有地區有搞好撚成功，個個親中辦事處都十號風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完完全全對到個政權準一準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪頭就搞大型中資/大型連鎖藍店同福建幫，藍絲小店就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多兩個月乖乖地無人食自動收皮架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我尋日一見18區第一個反應就係搵哂所有依啲仆街嘅辦事處係邊，見佢地咁up dup真係想同佢老尾裝修好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望大家會將佢地放係checklist第一位，鋪頭裝修唔切唔緊要，偉大嘅議員做左咁多地區工作一定要我地調返轉幫幫手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb719cd94cee9ada8db6607b125f680fe11cfa3","tid":1624654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3fe2019eace333baec9386bc64081f61cd7aebeb","tid":1624654,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有車人士召集區<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.5 黨鐵和你塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b31e08c3b4353fb37f6cb4b8f6a42c6043abf8a","tid":1624654,"uid":60423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"你地最鐘意嘅對準政權呀"},{"pid":"ab3e1098f67f2e64c3a29b324e289245613d99fb","tid":1624654,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"蛇齋餅傻啲仆街呀"},{"pid":"10c1cde8ddd920c00ce22b49d9e3e04d0b5a24a2","tid":1624654,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,